# LIVE OTX Threat Intelligence Aggregator

Realtids pipeline som fångar MacSync infostealer IOCs från AlienVault OTX.

[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.8+-blue)](https://python.org)
[![OTX](https://img.shields.io/badge/OTX-Live-red)](https://otx.alienvault.com)

## What it does

LIVE: MacSync infostealer (28 IOCs realtime) [Jan 22 2026]

## Features

- LIVE OTX API - Pulser från AlienVault OTX
- 28 MacSync IOCs - Domains, IPs, file hashes  
- SIEM-ready JSON - Elasticsearch/Splunk-kompatibel
- Production error handling - Retry logic + logging
- YARA export - Malware detection rules

## Demo Output

```json
{
